(908, 9, 'description', 'Paper and Pixel is a boutique supplier of inventive table decorations and paper sculpture for weddings and events.\r\n\r\nPaper &amp; Pixel is a boutique supplier of inventive decorations for wedding receptions and events. We offer both off-the-shelf and custom designs to suit your theme. We create table decorations, lamps and paper sculpture that are unique in the market. Many can be customised with names. If you are sick of conventional flowers and vases on the table, we can help!\r\n\r\nPaper and Pixel also design and produce pop-up and shaped invitations, give aways and other print collateral for product launches and events.\r\n\r\n<strong>Table Decorations:</strong>\r\n\r\nSkyscraper One: Art Deco building with a light inside for added drama\r\n\r\nHeart pretzel- comes in pink or red customised with names on the mat below.\r\n\r\nPaper Baskets: you choose the colour!\r\n\r\nBud Vase (One ) with Menu panels\r\n\r\nBud Vases (Three ) with Menu panels\r\n\r\nPaper Waves\r\n\r\n<strong>Handbound Guest Books</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Other Products:</strong>\r\n\r\nPaper Sculpture Lamps: from $120.00-1500.00 each + GST depending on volume, size and complexity.\r\n\r\nCustom Paper Sculpture for Room Decorations: Prices on request.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Delivery</strong>: Decorations are boxed and couriered or hand delivered in the Sydney area. For customers outside of Sydney, NSW, extra packing is added. Transport costs are additional and will be clarified at time of ordering, depending on volume and distance.\r\n\r\n<strong>Lead Time</strong>: 4 weeks. Please order as soon as you have your dates so we can reserve decorations for you. Email or call us with last minute orders. We are happy to help depending on what we have in stock!'),
