(1208, 11, 'description', '<strong><em>Specialising in live music for wedding ceremonies and the bridal waltz</em></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>By Special Request is a boutique entertainment company specialising in providing live music to the more intimate moments of a wedding or special occasion. This includes wedding ceremonies and the bridal waltz, commitment ceremonies, naming ceremonies and baptisms, milestone birthday functions and other special occasions.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>So when you''re walking down the aisle, signing the marriage register, dancing the bridal waltz or celebrating another special occasion, By Special Request will ensure these moments are unforgettable by providing live singing suited to the occasion. </em>\r\n\r\n<em>By Special Request understands that each occasion is unique and will be cherished forever. That''s why By Special Request works with you personally to tailor a music program that captures what''s important to you, what works with the theme of the day and will leave a lasting impression with your guests.</em>'),
