(1844, 15, 'description', 'A Qualified and Experienced Wedding Planner, taking every step with you, saving you time and money, taking the stress away and putting the FUN back into planning the most important Event of your life.\r\n\r\nThink:  what value is it that you give your clients.  Why would they hire you.  What is your biggest point(s) of difference and value you give to clients that hire you ?  What areas do you service? What sort of lead time do you need (or don’t need, maybe last minute deals are your specialties).   Remember the type of people that will be seeing the page are venues / venue managers coordinators and customers, that are referred by each other / seen at trade shows.   So I suggest you do your paragraph to attract these type of customers.  I highly suggest doing it in numbered / bullet point form and making it easy to read.\r\n\r\nAt Soirees Events we treat each Bride as if it were one of us getting married, by being personable, building a relationship with the Bride and Groom, their families and Bridal Parties and being an extension of their foresight.\r\n\r\nWe deliver on what we promise, have high attention to detail and communicate with our client every step of the way, so that there are no surprises.\r\n\r\nWe service the whole of NSW, particularly Sydney but if transport is paid for then we are happy to plan an offshore wedding for instance.\r\n\r\nWe are able to plan your Wedding up to 1 year out and plan all aspects thereof, alternatively we could plan the parts of your Wedding that you find most challenging, could be enlisted in the week leading up to your special day and most importantly be your On The Day Wedding Consultant.\r\n\r\nAs a Wedding Planner we can save you money with our contacts and experience,  can negotiate with wedding vendors on your behalf,  offer professional guidance as we know the latest trends and we can help you to get things done quickly as we have existing contacts and systems'),
